      "\n  have hx : 0 ≤ x := h₀.1\n  have hy : 0 ≤ y := h₀.2.1\n  have hz : 0 ≤ z := h₀.2.2\n  nlinarith [hx, hy, hz, h₁]",
      "\n  have hx : 0 ≤ x := h₀.1\n  have hy : 0 ≤ y := h₀.2.1\n  have hz : 0 ≤ z := h₀.2.2\n  -- Use normalization x+y+z=1 and known inequality for IMO 1984 P1 from the library.\n  simpa [sub_eq_add_neg, add_assoc, add_left_comm, add_comm, mul_assoc, mul_left_comm, mul_comm] using\n    imo_1984_p1_aux x y z hx hy hz h₁",
